label: ObservationResult
comment: A collection of diagnostic data, visual or technical, and processing data, performed on a sample.

datatypeProperties.comment: The date, time, date time, or other date time value for the end of the observation for this sample observation result.
The date, time, date time, or other date time value for the start of the observation for this sample observation result.
The indication of whether or not the observation was an emergency observation for this sample observation result.
A general characteristic, such as length, volume, density, sensitivity, conductivity, expressed as text, of this specified inspection result.
The context material type of the observed sample, expressed as text, such as animal or blood.
The code specifying a material type for this sample observation result.
The observation discontinuation reason, expressed as text, for this sample observation result.
The code specifying the observation discontinuation reason for this sample observation result.
The observation time frame, expressed as text, for this sample observation result.
The indication of whether or not the observation was an outsourced observation (performed by a third party).
The indication of whether or not this sample observation result characteristic is shareable.

objectProperties.comment: A method applicable to this specified inspection result.
A note attached to the laboratory observation results with additional observations and or conclusions.
The laboratory observation party who authorized this sample observation result.
An expected value for the characteristic, to be observed or measured according to the specified type of observation for this sample observation result.
An applicable objective observation parameter of the interpretation result for this inspection result characteristic.
A laboratory observation analysis request reference specified for this sample observation result.
A maximum standard value of the values for the characteristic observed or measured by using the specified type of observation for this sample observation result.
A minimum standard value of the values for the characteristic observed or measured by using the specified type of observation for this sample observation result.
An observed value for the characteristic, acquired by observing or measuring according to the specified type of observation for this sample observation result.
The outsourced laboratory party who performed this sample observation result.
A set of laboratory observation instructions specified for this sample observation result.
A laboratory observation reference specified for this sample observation result.
A laboratory observation analysis method used for this sample observation result.

referencedBy.comment: A laboratory sample observation result for this specified inspection result.
